<tal:block xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
           xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
           i18n:domain="gs.group.member.join"
           define="adminInfo options/adminInfo | view/loggedInUserInfo;
                   userInfo options/userInfo | view/loggedInUserInfo;
                   userEmail options/userEmail | view/userEmailInfo"
           i18n:translate="new-member-msg-txt">Dear <tal:block i18n:name="adminName" content="adminInfo/name">Admin</tal:block>,

<tal:block i18n:name="memberName"
           content="userInfo/name">A new member</tal:block> has joined
<tal:block i18n:name="groupName"
           content="view/groupInfo/name">this group</tal:block>.

  * View the profile for <tal:block i18n:name="memberName" content="userInfo/name">the new member</tal:block> at
    <tal:block i18n:name="groupURL" content="string:${view/siteInfo/url}${userInfo/url}">URL</tal:block>

  * View the membership of <tal:block i18n:name="groupName" content="view/groupInfo/name">this group</tal:block> at
    <tal:block i18n:name="membershipURL" content="string:${view/groupInfo/url}/membership.html">URL</tal:block>

You are received this message because you are an administrator  of
<tal:block i18n:name="groupName" content="view/groupInfo/name">This Group</tal:block>.

Kind regards
  The <tal:block i18n:name="siteName" content="view/siteInfo/name">Site</tal:block> Team

------------------------------------------------------------------------

